Useful tool for improving the &quot;material&quot; needs of folk, to encourage innovation, intercourse and change, but thats it, it's not good for yer country's political or moral systems when it's held as the be all and end all. <br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Dog eat dog, might is right, winners rule</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> is NOT good for folks.<br>
Encouraging innovation, hard work, skill etc is good, so is making sure that all people are wlel educated and healthy as that stops epidemics (disease is NO respector of wealth) and ignorance (dumb populace is a POOR populace ESPECIALLY today and in the future)<br>
